snippet.title: Best VGM 636 - Phantasy Star Portable 2 - Fly to Universe
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PSP
Phantasy Star Portable 2 (2010)
Fly to Universe
Hideaki Kobayashi
